            </h1>
            <p className=\"mt-5 max-w-xl text-slate-600 text-base leading-relaxed\">
              Paste a job description, drop resumes, and get an explainable score breakdown across
              skills, experience, education, and culture fit — powered by Claude Sonnet 4.5.
            </p>
            <div className=\"mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3\">
              <Link to=\"/jobs/new\" data-testid=\"hero-new-job-btn\" className=\"btn-primary\">
                <Plus size={16} weight=\"bold\" /> Create a job
              </Link>
              <Link to=\"/jobs\" data-testid=\"hero-view-jobs-btn\" className=\"btn-secondary\">
                Browse jobs <ArrowRight size={16} />
              </Link>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div className=\"md:col-span-4 border-l border-slate-200 md:pl-8\">
            <div className=\"overline mb-3\">HOW IT WORKS</div>
            <ol className=\"space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-700 font-mono\">
              <li className=\"flex gap-3\">
                <span className=\"w-6 h-6 border border-slate-300 flex items-center justify-center text-xs\">01</span>
                Define the role & required skills.
              </li>
              <li className=\"flex gap-3\">
                <span className=\"w-6 h-6 border border-slate-300 flex items-center justify-center text-xs\">02</span>
                Upload PDFs or add candidates manually.
              </li>
              <li className=\"flex gap-3\">
                <span className=\"w-6 h-6 border border-slate-300 flex items-center justify-center text-xs\">03</span>
                Run TalentRank AI and read the reasoning.
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Stats */}
      <section>
        <div className=\"flex items-baseline justify-between mb-4\">
          <h2 className=\"font-display text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Signal</h2>
          <span className=\"font-mono text-xs text-slate-500\">live · {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</span>
